comment_data.body:
That particular combination is not supported yet. We're working on a new version for AS 4.0 beta, which should be available soon. The M44 testing feedback issue might be of interest: #4403. It will be closed when the next version is published.

If you can accept some risk, you can switch to the dev channel, which works better for AS 4.0. Instructions are here:
https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/flutter-announce/tTgQcTgqrKg
Thanks, for the info and for the links.

title: Several tracebacks in Android Studio 4.0 Beta 1
